OL,3,CLondon's roads worst in Europe for
OL,4,Ctraffic and delays
OL,6,FLondon's roads were the most congested
OL,7,Fin Europe last year, according to new
OL,8,Fanalysis.
OL,10,FTransport analytics company Inrix said
OL,11,Fdrivers in the capital spent 101 hours
OL,12,Fsitting in traffic in 2024, a 2%
OL,13,Fincrease from the previous year.
OL,15,FThe total cost to London was estimated
OL,16,Fat #3.85 billion, at an average of
OL,17,F#942 per driver.
