OL,3,CLondon's roads worst in Europe for
OL,4,Ctraffic and delays
OL,6,FParis had the second most clogged-up
OL,7,Froads in Europe in 2024 with 97 hours
OL,8,Fof delays per driver, followed by
OL,9,FDublin (81 hours).
OL,11,FLondon was ranked the fifth most
OL,12,Fcongested city in the world, with
OL,13,FIstanbul in first place.
OL,15,FAcross the UK, the average driver
OL,16,Fspent 62 hours in congestion last
OL,17,Fyear, an increase of one hour from
OL,18,F2023.
