OL,3,CLondon's roads worst in Europe for
OL,4,Ctraffic and delays
OL,6,FBob Pishue, Inrix transportation
OL,7,Fanalyst and author of the report,
OL,8,Fsaid: "While the UK did see a slight
OL,9,Fincrease in congestion again this
OL,10,Fyear, overall congestion has remained
OL,11,Fsteady.
OL,13,F"Roadworks in key corridors such as
OL,14,FM25 Wisely interchange caused
OL,15,Fconsiderable traffic on a main artery
OL,16,Finto the capital.
OL,18,F"Interestingly it was cities outside
OL,19,Fof the capital that saw the greatest
OL,20,Fincrease in congestion with Manchester
OL,21,Fseeing a large increase, up 13%.
