OL,3,CLondon's roads worst in Europe for
OL,4,Ctraffic and delays
OL,6,F"While London only had a modest
OL,7,Fincrease in time lost, it still
OL,8,Frepresented half of the entire
OL,9,Fcountry's delay."
OL,11,FInrix said London contained most of
OL,12,Fthe worst corridors for traffic delays
OL,13,Fin the UK because of the
OL,14,F"concentration of population,
OL,15,Femployment and economic activity".
