OL,3,CLondon's roads worst in Europe for
OL,4,Ctraffic and delays
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Transport for
OL,7,FLondon, which is responsible for a
OL,8,Fnetwork of red route roads carrying a
OL,9,Fthird of the capital's traffic, said:
OL,10,F"We are committed to making sure
OL,11,FLondoners can move around the capital
OL,12,Fas safely, sustainably and efficiently
OL,13,Fas possible.
OL,15,F"We support the movement of everyone
OL,16,Facross London and our investment in
OL,17,Fwalking, cycling and public transport
OL,18,Fis making it easier to choose
OL,19,Fsustainable ways of travelling,
OL,20,Fhelping to cut congestion.
